args: We've got trouble! There are more\nfiends coming from that direction!
MORE?! How many times is this?!
I hate to ask this of you when we're all\nexhausted, but we need to keep going\nfor just a little bit longer!
(And how much longer will I have to\nwait to finally catch him alone?!)
Alas, Ezelith's laments did nothing to stop the\nfiends from pressing their attack.
Having to fight this many battles\nin a row is rough...
Are you okay?! Keep it together!
Don't worry about me. This is nothing.
Oh nooo! We've got more fiends\ncoming from over that hill!
We need to fight them off and\nprotect the villagers. Let's go!
(If these damned fiends didn't show up,\nthis would have gone perfectly!)
This is all your stupid fault!
You're doing this on purpose, aren't you?\nYou're getting in my way ON PURPOSE!
NO EXCUSES! You're going to pay!
Whoa. She's seriously scary right now.
You're telling me—but we've got to fight\njust as hard. Follow her lead!
We did it! The fiends are gone!
That big lug Ezelith just took out must've\nbeen their leader.
Good work, everyone. Thanks to all of you,\nwe kept that village safe.
Thank you for the help, Ezelith. *rumble*
Heh. I guess I'm hungry after all that.
That's no surprise—you didn't even have\nlunch before heading out to battle.
In that case, why don't you have this?
Are these chocolates? Oh, thank you!
Yeah! It tastes like there's dried fruits\nand nuts inside it, too.
The level of sweetness takes away your\nfatigue, but all the textures really make\nit interesting to eat.
Hey! Gimme a bite of that!
I would also like to try these chocolates,\nif it isn't too much trouble.
The two of you are forbidden from taking\nso much as a single nibble.
Hey! Ya want me to waste away\nover here?
Yeah. Heck, it was thanks to all of you that\nI even thought of making it to begin with.
I suppose I could stand to give you all\na bit of thanks at least once a year!
The chocolate cake you made the other\nday was exceptional, but this has a\ncertain charm all its own.
I was exhausted before having this,\nbut now I'm totally full of beans again!
You're right. It just took a single bite.
Well, um...I'm glad. I DID put a lot of\neffort into them, after all.
We should start takin' these chocolates\nwith us when we go out on patrol.
I agree. Plus, they are nice and small,\nso they won't weigh us down.
In that case, I shall work on preparing\nsome for future expeditions.
Might you teach me the recipe, Ezelith?
This will be reassuring to have when we\ngo out to fight. Thank you, Ezelith.
(That ended up going nothing like\nI planned it to, but...)
(I think I ended up learning a lot from\neveryone through all this.)
Yeah. I think that was for the best.
Hee hee! Nope! Nothing at all.
Now fill yourself up with my special\nchocolates and keep on fighting!
